trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Accessibility.IAccessibleHandler" /> and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) accessibility interface.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:Accessibility.IAccessibleHandler" /> e todos os seus membros expostos fazem parte de um wrapper gerenciado da interface de acessibilidade COM (Component Object Model).

trans-unit.source: For more information about <xref:Accessibility._RemotableHandle>, see the [Microsoft Active Accessibility](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/dd373592(v=vs.85).aspx) documentation.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre <xref:Accessibility._RemotableHandle>, consulte o [Microsoft Active Accessibility](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/dd373592(v=vs.85).aspx) documentação.
